---
export const prerender = true;
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<style is:global>
.faq-wrap { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 48px 20px 80px; }
.faq-section-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(20px,4vw,26px); font-weight: 700; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 24px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--pink-pale); }
.faq-group { margin-bottom: 52px; }
details { background: white; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); box-shadow: var(--shadow-card); margin-bottom: 10px; overflow: hidden; }
details[open] { box-shadow: 0 4px 32px rgba(255,107,157,.12); }
summary { padding: 20px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; color: var(--dark); cursor: pointer; list-style: none; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; }
summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
summary::after { content: '+'; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--pink); flex-shrink: 0; line-height: 1; transition: transform .25s; }
details[open] summary::after { transform: rotate(45deg); }
summary:hover { color: var(--pink); }
.faq-answer { padding: 0 20px 20px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--mid); font-weight: 300; }
.faq-answer p { margin-bottom: 10px; }
.faq-answer p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
.faq-answer a { color: var(--pink); }
.faq-contact-strip { background: var(--pink-pale); border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,107,157,.2); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 28px 24px; text-align: center; margin-top: 56px; }
.faq-contact-strip p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--mid); margin-bottom: 16px; }
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .faq-wrap { padding: 64px 40px 100px; }
  summary { padding: 22px 24px; font-size: 16px; }
  .faq-answer { padding: 0 24px 24px; font-size: 15px; }
}
</style>

<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  title="FAQ | Creative Solace | Rhinestone Kits and Workshops"
  description="Answers to common questions about Creative Solace rhinestone canvas kits, B7000 adhesive, workshop bookings, shipping, returns, and events in the Netherlands."
  canonical="https://creativesolace.com/faq"
  ogTitle="FAQ | Creative Solace"
  ogDescription="Everything you need to know about our rhinestone kits, workshops, shipping, and returns."
  ogUrl="https://creativesolace.com/faq"
  hreflangEn="https://creativesolace.com/faq"
  hreflangNl="https://creativesolace.com/nl/faq"
  heroLabel="Help"
  heroTitle="Frequently asked"
  heroTitleEm="questions"
  heroSub="Everything you need to know about our kits, workshops, orders, and returns. Can not find your answer? Email us at hello@creativesolace.com."
  breadcrumb="FAQ"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "FAQPage",
      "mainEntity": [
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "What comes in the rhinestone kit?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Every kit includes a premium printed canvas with 4 cm gallery-wrap border, all the rhinestones you need to complete the design, an applicator pen, a wax tray, and a tube of B7000 professional adhesive. Everything is included. You do not need to buy anything extra." } },
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Why do your kits use B7000 glue instead of a sticky canvas?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "B7000 creates a permanent bond. Once the glue cures (24 to 48 hours), the stones are fixed for good. A sticky canvas can lose its grip over time, especially in warm rooms." } },
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Is this suitable for beginners?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. That is exactly who it is designed for. If you can hold a pen, you can do this. No creative experience is needed at all." } },
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "How quickly do you ship?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Orders are packed and shipped within 1 to 3 business days. You will receive a shipping confirmation email with a track and trace link once your order is on its way." } },
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Is shipping free in the Netherlands?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. Shipping is free on all orders within the Netherlands. For international orders, shipping costs are calculated at checkout." } },
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Can I return my kit?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. You have 14 days from the date of delivery to return an unused kit in its original condition with the B7000 seal intact. Return shipping costs are your responsibility." } },
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Do I need experience to join a workshop?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "None at all. Our workshops are designed for people who have never painted or bedazzled before. We guide you through everything step by step." } },
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "How do I book a workshop?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Click the Book a Workshop button on our website and fill in the short form. We will get back to you within 24 hours to confirm availability and details." } },
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Where do workshops take place?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "We can come to your home, your venue, or a location of your choice. The location is always confirmed during the booking process." } },
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "My order arrived damaged. What do I do?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Take a photo of the damage and email it to hello@creativesolace.com within 72 hours of delivery. Include your order number. We will sort it out for you." } }
      ]
    })}</script>
  </Fragment>

  <div class="faq-wrap">

    <div class="faq-group">
      <h2 class="faq-section-title">About the Kits</h2>
      <details>
        <summary>What comes in the kit?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Every kit includes a premium printed canvas with a 4 cm gallery-wrap border (ready to hang without a frame), all the rhinestones you need to complete the design, an applicator pen, a wax tray, and a tube of B7000 professional adhesive. Everything is included. You do not need to buy anything extra.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Is this the same as diamond painting?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Similar but not the same. Classic diamond painting uses a sticky canvas with a pre-set grid. Our kits use a freestyle approach with B7000 adhesive, so you have more control over where you place each stone. The result looks bolder, more textured, and more like real wall art.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Why B7000 glue and not a sticky canvas?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>B7000 creates a permanent bond. Once the glue cures (24 to 48 hours), the stones are fixed for good. A sticky canvas can lose its grip over time, especially in warm rooms. The precision tip on the B7000 tube also lets you be more deliberate and accurate with your placement.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Do I need to frame it?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>No. The canvas has a 4 cm gallery-wrap border, which means the edges are clean and finished. It looks great hung directly on the wall without a frame.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>How long does it take to complete?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Most people finish in 3 to 6 hours spread over a few sessions. It is a relaxing activity, not a race. Many people do it while watching TV or listening to a podcast.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Is it suitable for beginners?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. That is exactly who it is designed for. If you can hold a pen, you can do this. No creative experience is needed.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>How do I look after the finished piece?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>After the glue has fully cured (24 to 48 hours), the stones are very secure. If the canvas needs cleaning, use a soft dry brush or a lint-free cloth. Do not spray water or cleaning products directly on the surface.</p></div>
      </details>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-group">
      <h2 class="faq-section-title">Orders and Shipping</h2>
      <details>
        <summary>How quickly do you ship?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Orders are packed and shipped within 1 to 3 business days of payment. You will receive a confirmation email with a track and trace link once your order is dispatched.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Is shipping free in the Netherlands?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. Shipping is free on all orders within the Netherlands. For orders to Belgium, Germany, or the rest of Europe, shipping costs are calculated at checkout before you pay.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Can I change or cancel my order?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>You have 24 hours from the time of purchase to request a change or cancellation. After that, your order will already be in processing. Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@creativesolace.com">hello@creativesolace.com</a> as quickly as possible if you need to make a change.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>What if I entered the wrong shipping address?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@creativesolace.com">hello@creativesolace.com</a> within 24 hours of placing your order. If your package has already been shipped, we are not able to redirect it.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>My order arrived damaged. What do I do?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Take a photo of the damage and email it to <a href="mailto:hello@creativesolace.com">hello@creativesolace.com</a> within 72 hours of delivery. Include your order number. We will arrange a replacement or refund at no cost to you.</p><p>Note: minor dents to the outer box that do not affect the product inside do not qualify for replacement.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Can I return my kit?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. Under EU consumer law you have the right to return your purchase within 14 days of delivery, without giving a reason. The kit must be unused and in its original packaging with the B7000 seal intact. Return shipping costs are your responsibility.</p><p>Email <a href="mailto:hello@creativesolace.com">hello@creativesolace.com</a> with your order number to start a return. See our <a href="/shipping">Shipping and Returns page</a> for full details.</p></div>
      </details>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-group">
      <h2 class="faq-section-title">Workshops and Events</h2>
      <details>
        <summary>Do I need experience to join a workshop?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>None at all. Our workshops are designed for people who have never painted or bedazzled before. We guide you through everything step by step.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>How do I book a workshop?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Click the Book a Workshop button on our website and fill in the short form. We will get back to you within 24 hours to confirm availability and details.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Can I book a private workshop for my group?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. We specialise in private events for birthdays, bachelorette parties, and corporate team sessions. Fill in the quote form or email us at <a href="mailto:hello@creativesolace.com">hello@creativesolace.com</a> and we will put together a custom package.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Where do workshops take place?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>We can come to your home, your venue, or a location of your choice anywhere in the Netherlands. For some open public workshops we host at our own venue. The exact location is always confirmed when you book.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>How many people can join a workshop?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Paint and Sip: 6 to 25 people. Bedazzle and Sip: 6 to 20 people. Private events and corporate sessions can be customised based on your group size. Contact us for larger groups.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>I bought a ticket for an event. Where do I find it?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Your ticket is sent to your email address immediately after purchase. It includes a unique code and a QR code. Bring it on your phone or print it out. We scan it at the door.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Are workshop tickets refundable?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Workshop and event tickets are non-refundable once purchased, unless the event is cancelled by Creative Solace. If we cancel, you will receive a full refund within 14 days.</p><p>If you booked via our quote form and can no longer attend, email us as soon as possible and we will do our best to find an alternative date.</p></div>
      </details>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-contact-strip">
      <p>Still have a question? We are happy to help.</p>
      <a href="mailto:hello@creativesolace.com" class="btn-primary">Email us at hello@creativesolace.com</a>
    </div>

  </div>

</BaseLayout>
